1. install git
2. Git recipe
    Go to http://github.com/zerok/zerokspot.gitrecipe/tree/master
    open a shell and run :
    $> git clone http://github.com/zerok/zerokspot.gitrecipe/tree/master zerokspot-gitrecipe
    $> cd zerokspot-gitrecipe
    $> sudo port install py-setuptools
    $> python setup.py install
3. Run buildout
    Go to milkshape directory
    $> python bootstrap.py
    $> ./bin/buildout
